so / Canada</dd><dt><a href="/sight-and-sound/greatest-films-all-time/all-voters/will-sloan">Will Sloan</a></dt><dd>Canada</dd><dt><a href="/sight-and-sound/greatest-films-all-time/all-voters/gerwin-tamsma">Gerwin Tamsma</a></dt><dd>Netherlands</dd><dt><a href="/sight-and-sound/greatest-films-all-time/all-voters/anne-thompson">Anne Thompson</a></dt><dd>USA</dd><dt><a href="/sight-and-sound/greatest-films-all-time/all-voters/alexandru-tirdea">Alexandru Tirdea</a></dt><dd>Romania</dd><dt><a href="/sight-and-sound/greatest-films-all-time/all-voters/peter-tonguette">Peter Tonguette</a></dt><dd>USA</dd><dt><a href="/sight-and-sound/greatest-films-all-time/all-voters/ivan-velisavljevic">Ivan Velisavljević</a></dt><dd>Serbia</dd><dt><a href="/sight-and-sound/greatest-films-all-time/all-voters/christian-viviani">Christian VIVIANI</a></dt><dd>France</dd><dt><a href="/sight-and-sound/greatest-films-all-time/all-voters/michael-wood">Michael Wood</a></dt><dd>USA</dd></dl></section><section><h3>Directors</h3><dl><dt><a href="/sight-and-sound/greatest-films-all-time/all-voters/mark-cousins">Mark Cousins</a></dt><dd>UK</dd><dt><a href="/sight-and-sound/greatest-films-all-time/all-voters/abel-ferrara">Abel Ferrara</a></dt><dd>USA</dd><dt><a href="/sight-and-sound/greatest-films-all-time/all-voters/amos-gitai">Amos Gitai</a></dt><dd>Israel/France </dd><dt><a href="/sight-and-sound/greatest-films-all-time/all-voters/owen-kline">Owen Kline</a></dt><dd>USA</dd><dt><a href="/sight-and-sound/greatest-films-all-time/all-voters/lluis-minarro">Lluís Miñarro</a></dt><dd>Spain</dd><dt><a href="/sight-and-sound/greatest-films-all-time/all-voters/frank-oz">Frank Oz</a></dt><dd>USA</dd><dt><a href="/sight-and-sound/greatest-films-all-time/all-voters/lindsey-vickers">Lindsey Vickers</a></dt><dd>UK</dd></dl></section></div></details><div class="ArticleGrid__Outer-sc-nctj0m-0 iIGxlL article_grid_block"><h2 class="Headline__H2-sc-e1fxl5-2 eKkqcD ArticleGrid__StyledHeadline-sc-nctj0m-3 dQGFXG" aria-l